POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "testuser"
}

### Authenticate User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/authenticate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "testuser"
}

### Tournament Endpoints

# Get All Tournaments (requires x-user-id header)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tournaments
x-user-id: {{userId}}

### Create Tournament (requires x-user-id header)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tournaments
Content-Type: application/json
x-user-id: {{userId}}

{
  "name": "Test Tournament",
  "description": "A test tournament",
  "max_num": 8,
  "rule": "simple"
}

### Get Tournament by ID (replace {id} with actual tournament ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tournaments/{id}
x-user-id: {{userId}}

### Open Tournament (replace {id} with actual tournament ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tournaments/{id}/open
x-user-id: {{userId}}

### Get Tournament Participants (replace {id} with actual tournament ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tournaments/{id}/participants
x-user-id: {{userId}}

### Join Tournament (replace {id} with actual tournament ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tournaments/{id}/join
Content-Type: application/json
x-user-id: {{userId}}

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}"
}

### Battle Endpoints

# Ready for Battle (PUT method, requires tournament ID in URL)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tournaments/{tournamentId}/battle/ready
x-user-id: {{userId}}

### Cancel Battle
POST {{baseUrl}}/battle/cancel
Content-Type: application/json
x-user-id: {{userId}}

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "battleId": "test-battle"
}

### AI Opponent
POST {{baseUrl}}/battle/ai-opponent
Content-Type: application/json
x-user-id: {{userId}}

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "aiLevel": 1
} 
